<annotation id="annotation_1232598849" type="text" style="popup" log_data="a-id=annotation_1232598849&amp;a-type=1&amp;xble=1&amp;a-v=twcHuKYR0pY&amp;ei=wbceXNTiMtLa8gTni5boAg" itct="CAEQs-UBGP___________wEiEwiUx6W7u7TfAhVSrZwKHeeFBS0o-B0yAml2SJalx7CK98GDtwE">
  <TEXT>Strangely enough, for whatever reason, the selection highlight on the RM screen always starts you off on the top left. In those regards, while Crypt Man is a good place to start, I prefer going after Fuse Man first. Simply put - he has the best weapon in the game, and I want it as soon as possible.</TEXT>
  <segment>
    <movingRegion type="rect">
      <rectRegion x="0.00000" y="0.00000" w="100.00000" h="25.22500" t="3:24.160"/>
      <rectRegion x="0.00000" y="0.00000" w="100.00000" h="25.22500" t="3:38.200"/>
    </movingRegion>
  </segment>
  <appearance bgAlpha="0.600000023842" bgColor="0" fgColor="16777215" textSize="3.911599999999999" effects="">
    
